quotes.author: Charles R. Swindoll
quotes.quote: Life is 10% what happens to you and 90% how you react to it.

quotes.author: Norman Vincent Peale
quotes.quote: Change your thoughts, and you change your world.

quotes.author: Walt Disney
quotes.quote: All our dreams can come true if we have the courage to pursue them.

quotes.author: Ben Sweetland
quotes.quote: Success is a journey not a destination.

quotes.author: Zig Ziglar
quotes.quote: What you get by achieving your goals is not as important as what you become by achieving your goals.

quotes.author: Nelson Mandela
quotes.quote: It always seems impossible until it's done.

quotes.author: Maya Angelou
quotes.quote: Success is liking yourself, liking what you do, and liking how you do it.

quotes.author: W. Clement Stone
quotes.quote: Aim for the moon. If you miss, you may hit a star.

quotes.author: Napoleon Hill
quotes.quote: If you cannot do great things, do small things in a great way.

quotes.author: Mallika Tripathi
quotes.quote: Success only comes to those who dare to attempt.

quotes.author: Estée Lauder
quotes.quote: I never dreamed about success. I worked for it.

quotes.author: Milton Berle
quotes.quote: If opportunity doesn't knock, build a door.

quotes.author: Nina Simone
quotes.quote: You’ve got to learn to leave the table when love’s no longer being served.

quotes.author: Gary Zukav
quotes.quote: Scarcity of self-value cannot be remedied by money, recognition, affection, attention, or influence.

quotes.author: Brené Brown
quotes.quote: Talk to yourself like someone you love.

quotes.author: Lucille Ball
quotes.quote: Love yourself first and everything else falls into place.

quotes.author: Gabrielle Union
quotes.quote: If you prioritize yourself, you are going to save yourself.

quotes.author: E.E. Cummings
quotes.quote: It takes courage to grow up and become who you really are.

quotes.author: Toni Morrison
quotes.quote: You are your best thing.

quotes.author: Edwin Elliot
quotes.quote: By being yourself you put something wonderful in the world that was not there before.
